{"tid":1215482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港打工仔最佳嘅「反送中」活動","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T07:49:25.000Z","uid":260093,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1006a71290dd0741f3671ba275b2e36e857d1b","tid":1215482,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"無疑地，叫打工仔罷工罷到20號係好困難<br />\n與其罷工，不如慢做<br />\n老細唔炒得你，又耐你唔何<br />\n又可以長遠地消磨同拖慢香港經濟<br />\n所以希望大家幫手宣傳俾自己認識嘅打工仔<br />\n<br />\n「歡迎各位打工仔踴躍參與🙏順便將呢個活動分享俾你更多嘅朋友呀！」<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyNF11C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhyNF11C.png&h=5400146e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58e1fce70e5d64a84a67dbfa1c3d3e5d1a897126","tid":1215482,"uid":110895,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔好意思...<br />\n我諗呢個活動反映唔到啲乜...<br />\n因為我日日都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee1e38cab2c2685507e5afec808a8e68a0dd12e","tid":1215482,"uid":260093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58e1fce70e5d64a84a67dbfa1c3d3e5d1a897126","tid":1215482,"uid":110895,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"唔好意思...<br />\n我諗呢個活動反映唔到啲乜...<br />\n因為我日日都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"咁你可以再慢啲<br />\n主要係明白，支持嘅人入面有唔少打工仔<br />\n要佢哋罷工打咁耐係好困難<br />\n希望佢哋可以用另一種方式去參與<br />\n雖然反應唔到啲咩！<br />\n但做得小小得少少<br />\n所以唔該你🙏幫手分享出去啊！"},{"pid":"d275a872fac272e89570cd555920967df5d4eb01","tid":1215482,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"一年365日都做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe8c44c138aa70dc83e414d89c6e280c0b2aa12","tid":1215482,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"4062e8b4391a5a757531140a42e6ab3